      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUBELIN (1) showed blistering early speed from barrier sixteen when she led to the home turn before tiring to finish ninth over 1100m at Scone in C1 class. Can do much better here from the better draw. HONNIBALL DRIVE (6) was heavily supported late on debut with a fast-finishing second over 1000m at Gunnedah. Further improved for this and will appreciate the fast tempo. Leading player. HULALAND (3) slow into stride and chipped away late when ninth over 1100m at Scone in the LR Woodlands. Can bounce quickly today despite drawing out. MISS ANDREAS (9) well drawn today and improvement is anticipated third-up. Covered plenty of ground from the awkward gate and tired late when sixth over 1000m at Gunnedah. Maps well and has each way claims.",
